title: Understanding.Research.with.Access.Code.A.Consumers.Guide.2nd.ed
description:
Format: PDF
Genre: research/tutorial
Published: 2014

Book Description: This introductory text is written specifically for consumers of research - anyone who uses the results and implications of research studies to enhance their knowledge and improve their practice. The focus is on guiding students toward a basic understanding of the research process, allowing them to develop the skills, knowledge and strategies needed to read, interpret, and evaluate the quality of research reports. The text provides balanced coverage of quantitative, qualitative, and combined research approaches.
